  <summary date="2019-12-17T17:08:16Z" status="Introduced in House">License Transfer Modernization Act of 2019

This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission to approve or deny a license-transfer application within 180 days of submission. These applications relate to the transfer of control or assignment for radio-station licenses.</summary>
